# EAS Build upload ignore rules

# This prevents large local folders/caches from being included in the project archive.

# Dependencies

node_modules/

# Expo/Metro caches

.expo/
.metro-health-check\*

# Web builds

web-build/
dist/

# Native folders (generated)

android/
ios/

# Logs

npm-debug._
yarn-debug._
yarn-error.\*
\*.log

# Large binaries / archives (common accidental commits/downloads)

**/\*.apk
**/_.aab
\*\*/_.ipa
**/\*.zip
**/_.7z
\*\*/_.tar
**/\*.tar.gz
**/\*.tgz

# Large media (avoid accidentally bundling recordings)

**/\*.mp4
**/_.mov
\*\*/_.mkv
